1. *Trudna* se žena osećala prilično usamljeno. (The pregnant woman felt quite lonely.)

2. Često se pitam kako je *trudna* majka uspela da se izbori sa svim tim obavezama. (I often wonder how the pregnant mother managed to cope with all those duties.)

3. *Trudna* žena je otišla kod ginekologa da bi proverila zdravstveno stanje njene bebe. (The pregnant woman went to the gynecologist to check the health of her baby.)

4. *Trudna* supruga je veoma zabrinuta zbog njenog stanja. (The pregnant wife is very worried about her condition.)

5. Njena *trudna* sestra je bio trudna sa gemelima. (Her pregnant sister was pregnant with twins.)